                      <div class="media-body clearfix">
                        <h2>
                            Protect your joints
                        </h2>  
                          <div class="caption margin-24-bottom">The main thing Reininger teaches patients is to protect their joints, even those that are currently symptom-free.<br /><br />You should always be thinking about your joints, even when doing small tasks, she says. <br /><br />Instead of lifting a heavy pot, slide it across the counter; use a shoulder to open a door rather your hand; and hold books in the palm of your hands, not with your fingers.</div>
                    
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  
