                      <div class="media-body clearfix">
                        <h2>
                            Try a cane
                        </h2>  
                          <div class="caption margin-24-bottom">A lot of people think a cane signifies disability, but if it helps reduce joint pain, who cares?
                    <br /><br />Canes are easy to find and use and can take up to 20% of your body weight off of your legs, hips, and ankles.</div>
                    
