                      <div class="media-body clearfix">
                        <h2>
                            Lose weight
                        </h2>  
                          <div class="caption margin-24-bottom">Being overweight can place excessive stress on, and adversely affect, your weight-bearing joints like the knees, back, and hips, Reininger says. <br /><br />Studies have shown that fat tissue may produce chemicals that can increase inflammation, something rheumatoid arthritis patients need to avoid.</div>
                    
                      </div>
