                      <div class="slide-info">
                        <span class="counter">10 of 11</span>
                        <span class="credit"></span>
                      </div>
                    
                      <div class="media-body clearfix">
                        <h2>
                            Use special tools
                        </h2>  
                          <div class="caption margin-24-bottom">Certain types of equipment can help make everyday tasks less painful. Pens, knives, can openers, zipper pulls, and additional products are available to help you protect your joints, Reininger says. <br /><br />The good news about finding such equipment is that you don’t always have to look in specialty stores for them. <br /><br />Many tools are designed simply to make them easier to use&#151;kitchen tools with large handles, ergonomic can openers, and large drawer pulls.</div>
                    
                      </div>
                    </div>
